content: No guests match your search. Please adjust your search parameters or clear the search field to view the full list of guests.

comment.text: This translation key is used for a message that appears when no guests match the search criteria, prompting the user to adjust their search parameters or clear the search field. It is typically displayed on an empty screen in the Contacts section of a page.

usage.context:
: t("Common:NotFoundGuests")
 : t("Common:NotFoundMembers");
 
 const description = isEmptyGuests
 ? isFiltered
 ? t("Common:NotFoundFilterGuestsDescription")
 : t("Common:NotFoundGuestsDescription")
 : isEmptyGroup
 ? t("Common:EmptyGroupDescription")
 : t("Common:NotFoundUsersDescription");

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'لا بوجد' should be 'لا يوجد'.

The phrase "검색 매개변수를 조정하거나" is somewhat literal and could be phrased more naturally. A more common and user-friendly way to say 'adjust your search parameters' would be something like "검색 조건을 변경하거나" (change your search conditions).
The phrase 'ເຫັນດີກັບການຄົ້ນຫາຂອງທ່ານ' (hen dee gap kan khon haa khong khun) literally translates to 'agree with your search'. This doesn't accurately convey the meaning of 'match your search'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider using a phrase like 'ຖືກຕ້ອງຕາມການຄົ້ນຫາຂອງທ່ານ' (thuk tong taam kan khon haa khong khun) which means 'corresponds to your search' or 'matches your search'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'ລ້າງຄຳນຶ່ງການຄົ້ນຫາ' (laang kham neung kan khon haa) is awkward. 'ຄຳນຶ່ງ' isn't the correct word to use in this context. It means something like 'one word' or 'a word'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Replace with 'ລ້າງຄຳສຸ່ມການຄົ້ນຫາ' (laang kham sum kan khon haa) which means 'clear the search terms', or more simply 'ລ້າງການຄົ້ນຫາ' (laang kan khon haa) - 'clear the search'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "Niciunul dintre invitații nu se potrivește cu ceea ce căutați" is a bit awkward. A more natural phrasing would be something along the lines of "Niciun invitat nu se potrivește cu căutarea dumneavoastră." or "Nu s-au găsit invitați care să corespundă căutării dumneavoastră."
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nu s-au găsit invitați care să corespundă căutării dumneavoastră.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "Vă rugăm să configurați parametrii de căutare" could be improved. While technically correct, it's more formal than the original English. A more conversational and user-friendly phrasing would be better.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Vă rugăm să ajustați parametrii de căutare

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'අමුත්තන්' (amuttan) is slightly informal in this context. While not incorrect, a more formal term like 'හිතකරුවන්' (hitakaruwan) might be more appropriate for a user interface.
The phrase 'ඔබගේ සෙවුමට ගැලපෙන' (obage sewumato galappenen) could be slightly rephrased for better flow. It's grammatically correct, but sounds a little clunky.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider rephrasing to 'ඔබේ සෙවුමේදි' (obey sewumeyedi) or 'ඔබේ සෙවුමට අනුව' (obey sewumato anuv)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'гостију' (guests) is missing an acute accent. It should be 'гостију́'.
The English phrase "adjust your search parameters" is too literal. A more natural Turkish equivalent would be "arama kriterlerinizi değiştirin" or "aramayı genişletin".
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Aramanızla eşleşen konuk yok. Konukların tam listesini görüntülemek için lütfen aramayı genişletin veya arama alanını temizleyin.
